---
title: Crispy Cajun Chicken Sandwiches with Potato Wedges & Secret Sauce
description: Crispy chicken is always a recipe for success. Place it between two toasted buns, spread on our secret sauce (as spicy or as tame as you like), top it off with pickles, serve it with crispy potato wedges, and you’ve got quite the winning dinner. As we like to say: “Get in my belly!”
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/627168639cce40baeb04f3c2-0d5726ca.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/652e8f0c0adad327d2408cbb.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/crispy-cajun-chicken-sandwiches-652e8f0c0adad327d2408cbb
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 1160 kcal
  fat: 61 g
